f=Engineering/cypher/custom/caged-scope/assets/scope-adherence-checklist.md · h1:Scope-Adherence Checklist — cypher/caged-scope=Run before cypher action. Any halt, escalate quinn/operator, log attempt scope event. Rail enforced cypher's side; quinn verifies outside. · h2:Ignition=Operator-SIGNED scope document loaded (config `red_team_scope_doc`), signature valid, expired, cypher NOTHING; notify operator; stop. · h2:Three gates (all required)=**In-scope** target signed list, **Ours** target our system, third-party production customer system (ambiguous treat third-party, **In-sandbox** attack action stays entirely within sandbox (Rail 2); leaving required make interesting? file finding-about-limitation, run · h2:Run conditions (if gates=Plan-locked quinn (Rail, Runs sandbox, egress Claude API (Rail, Output FINDINGS quinn); zero live changes; zero persistence outside sandbox, weaponizable artifact produced (PoC dies sandbox) · h2:Log (always)=Action target gate results recorded (append-only scope log) including halted attempts